      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen delivers linear power through a Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The double-VANOS system has been recently calibrated for optimal cam phasing, and the rod bearings have been addressed to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly health. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate fatigue. While the exterior shows a light patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptionally sharp. A true enthusiast\u2019s tool optimized for corner-exit traction and high-speed stability.",
