      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's still got plenty of adventures left in it? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it's in really solid shape! It runs like a dream and has been well-loved, making it the perfect choice if you want a quality vehicle without paying those brand-new prices. It's clean, comfy, and ready for a new home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
